Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须保护遥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你保护就可以了
