Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是觉得很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样可爱的笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从那时候开始的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来保护她 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来保护遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是黛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？ 是不是打错了
