Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 是猫
