Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和你的时空没有相连着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说过去是不能被改变的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去关系很好 两人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在预料之上 时空不安定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉 很相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拉库里玛被香格里拉介入之前非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 和大家一起去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:21:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是说和爸爸的约会要取消了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 只是想和你说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 现在还喜欢妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把它当作我们两人之间的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…妈妈不能原谅爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去帮你问一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是约定是两人的秘密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这次的约会有什么地方想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想乘船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又是游览船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是乘过了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那缆车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不要逗你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个电话应该接通不了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 连着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是打给我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知哪个时空的我 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稍微听下我自言自语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我最喜欢的佑感到痛苦的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:22:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮助他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏日的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.29,0:24:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 最近又看到幽灵了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.27,0:24:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 鸦不是什么幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.60,0:25:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再一次好好听我们讲话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.71,0:25:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.79,0:25:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到另一个世界吗
